<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7035597>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Shells, operculum and radulae of Radomaniola curta montenegrensis subsp. nov. A, B, holotype (MNCN 15.05/200157). C, paratype (UGSB 19515). D, shell (UGSB 19043). E–J, paratypes (UGSB 19515). E, F, operculum (E, inner side; F, outer side). G, protoconch. H, portion of radula ribbon. I, central radular teeth. J, outer marginal teeth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7035597/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7035599>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Anatomy of Radomaniola curta montenegrensis subsp. nov. A–E, H, I, L, paratypes (UGSB 19515). F, G, J, K, UGSB 19043. A, ctenidium and osphradium. B, stomach. C, partial nervous system. D, F, pallial oviduct. E, G, bursa copulatrix and seminal receptacles. H, J, head of male and penis. I, K, penis. L, prostate gland." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7035599/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

